  <official_title>CLIMB Prospective Multicenter Registry Evaluating the Use of the PolarCath Peripheral Dilatation System (Boston Scientific) in the Treatment of Infrapopliteal Lesions in Patients With Critical Limb Ischemia (Rutherford 4 and 5).</official_title>
